{"tid":1305581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議大家唔好捧殺抽tvb 廣告廠商","createTime":"2019-07-11T01:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:28:58.000Z","uid":270291,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8754de08b26edb43692a8ba70f4df5e713faf396","tid":1305581,"uid":270291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"其實寶礦力真係一個好好例子<br />\n佢係中國market 唔細<br />\n唔好係唔係都吹奏人地係黃絲品牌<br />\n你咁搞一搞 邊度仲有人敢抽tvb 廣告<br />\n我地一路都係想比壓力係tvb 落廣告既公司<br />\n但唔係個個都想個brand 非藍即黃<br />\n<br />\n建議我地只狙擊繼續落廣告既brand<br />\n其他公司可能見輿論壓力唔落廣告又無明言係撐今次運動既<br />\n就唔需要再捧殺人地<br />\n在商言商<br />\n你見wiki wong 都唔再comment 政治就知business man 既mindset"},{"pid":"3fecf44650260603dcf495408e9aec91c2d2353f","tid":1305581,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"畀連登仔搞到唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf9c034b8489fc6085fca42fa7e987e997af209","tid":1305581,"uid":270291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d4911f2e3ed162b31e374892bf8501053b31423","tid":1305581,"uid":270291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fecf44650260603dcf495408e9aec91c2d2353f","tid":1305581,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"畀連登仔搞到唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:44:20.000Z","msg":"本身想抽而家又驚比大陸抵制<br />\n唔係人人好似大家咁勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e28f5dbb55eca1d26f715cb819d52381ef1f7b","tid":1305581,"uid":270291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:59:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb55dd0ec02162b76db50fc3f4f1a74773d7929e","tid":1305581,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"我想睇奶粉廠抽多啲，睇下佢地是咪食返大陸奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b7e9ee626d1185d216c455402e068ef39bf524","tid":1305581,"uid":270291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:14:47.000Z","msg":"from tg<br />\n請幫手廣傳<br />\n廣告界推多兩推就肯幫手ga la<br />\nbtw一定要頂到年尾呀！！！！<br />\n10月係所有客平時會簽下年既tvb commitment既時間 一簽就過百萬 幾球咁簽<br />\n依家好多廣告客都淆緊底 準備抽緊tvb廣告<br />\n利申好多行內資料但我唔想暴露身分<br />\n但呢個風要頂到十月 咁班客就會驚左而唔commit咁多錢落tvb(tvb黎緊一定出好多discount)<br />\n利申我唔係做PHD 但係係其他方面既行內人<br />\n<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ca4c5ed8add60fe1c52415ab60b63713948337","tid":1305581,"uid":278204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n商家一定有商業考慮, 負責落廣告嗰個都可能要同高層/ 總公司交代.<br />\n逼佢哋高調表態, 反而搞到佢哋好難做.<br />\n總之佢哋有抽起廣告就得啦, 本來目的都係想斷CCTVB水喉啫, 唔好又失咗焦變咗追捧/ 批鬥商家."},{"pid":"9ce4b43ec5fceffee00a3c63ec39da2da6a658c0","tid":1305581,"uid":270291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e690484030910b3be01f5785e4a20f104c6e90e","tid":1305581,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb55dd0ec02162b76db50fc3f4f1a74773d7929e","tid":1305581,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"我想睇奶粉廠抽多啲，睇下佢地是咪食返大陸奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"奶粉廠都有好多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}